    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1885-01-13T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1885-01-13T00:00:00-05:00" n="89" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d89">
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <head>No. 85.<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Reinberg</persName> to Mr. <persName type="to">Davis</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Guayaquil</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1885-01-13">
                            <hi rend="italic">January</hi> 13,
                            1885</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Julio Romano Santos, prisoner at Port Manta. Northern ports continue closed.
                        Government claims Santos is an Ecuadorian, and wants proofs of his American
                        citizenship.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>REINBERG.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
